Homepage: http://screenshotgun.com

Package: screenshotgun
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libqt5widgets5, libqt5network5
Description: Open cross-platform screenshoter with cloud support and server part
 With this application you can make screenshots, draw different figures or write text on them and then upload to:
 - screenshotgun.com
 - Dropbox
 - Google Drive
 - Yandex.Disk
